    "description": "Sri Chaitanya Capital India, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Instructional Designer for our Delhi operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Sri Chaitanya Capital India:\nSri Chaitanya Capital India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Conduct parent-teacher meetings and update parents on student performance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Content Creation\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Sri Chaitanya Capital India!",
